What data structure is pictured in <image 1>?

A. Singly linked list
B. Doubly linked list
C. Circularly linked list
D. Array
E. None of the other answers

The image depicts a singly linked list. Each node contains some data and a reference (pointer) to the next node in the sequence, with the last node pointing to null.

Therefore, the correct answer is:

A. Singly linked list
